    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-07-20T09:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-07-20T09:00:00-05:00" n="426"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d426">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">683.84A/7–2051: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Israel</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_DAC1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davis</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Department of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d426fn1">Repeated for information to Amman, Baghdad, Beirut,
                        Damascus, Cairo, Jidda, Jerusalem, London, and Paris.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tel Aviv</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-07-20T17:00:00+03:00"
                            >July 20, 1951—5 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>58. <gloss target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 14, July 9<note n="2"
                        xml:id="d426fn2">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_757">p. 757</ref>.</note> and
                        <gloss target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 2, July 3.<note n="3"
                        xml:id="d426fn3">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_742">p. 742</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_FonMin1">FonMin</gloss> stated today Israel has taken
                    initiative in providing conf with reps of Syria and has suggested fol
                    agenda;</p>
                <p>1. Settlement of outstanding issues in spirit of <gloss target="#t_SC1"
                        >SC</gloss> Res of 16 Nov 1948, 11 Aug 1949 and 18 May 1951 and
                    Israel-Syrian Gen Armistice Agreement.</p>
                <p>2. Coop between local auths on each side of frontier on matters of mutual concern
                    such as: <list>
                        <label>(1)</label>
                        <item>Public security.</item>
                        <label>(2)</label>
                        <item>Health.</item>
                        <label>(3)</label>
                        <item>Agriculture, etc.</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <p>3. Question of economic relations between Syria and Israel.</p>
                <p>4. Other questions agreed upon by two parties.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_DAC1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Davis</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
